   ```
   =COUNTIFS($C:$C,$C2,$B:$B,">=TIME(21,30,0)",$B:$B,"<=TIME(22,0,0)")
   ```
   This counts all rows where the Name matches and the time‑of‑day falls between 21:30 and 22:00, regardless of the date.
4. Save the workbook to the output folder, recalculate, reload with `data_only=True`, and print a few sample counts to verify they are populated.
